<img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105240PCs7n0irmgOWc1dE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105242IELidax6MYnceqCk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105242uTqfM9Asktz3SBp0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105243yYv4ctsaXWp1KiGB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105248MfQXPLGN4rtDZvlh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105249PJjtLUFpOYZb3o0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105250AvYy6B8KZLEDjVou.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105255CiBYydcKMIfr7GJX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801111052564uRHhzmSIsPO8QYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105256Dg6OdwYz2UtLuaCB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105259AnOa48s396rDSGoc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.335113\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105301Vvi6ePIGDQRHJhaF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105302Duj4rCdGU0tQRa9T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105302Wtf7JPCSH2pDzlmX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.glossy.co/connected-fashion/loreals-newest-wearable-tracks-skins-sun-damage-and-sells-sunscreen\" rel=\"nofollow\">欧莱雅推出了可追踪穿戴设备</a>，它可以追踪 UVA 和 UVB 射线。APP 上也会有可以购买的产品推荐，提供相关健康指标的追踪。 2016 年 欧莱雅曾免费发放过类似的设备： “My UV Patch” ，根据消费者的反馈重新设计改进。预计这套可穿戴设备的价格会低于 100 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111112107eUgY2DIbO9ofrSRC.png\" data-ratio=\"0.718526\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>Loewe 发布了一本与日本艺术家 Fumiko Imano 合作的全新画册。 </p><p>这本画册由荷兰名模 Saskia de Brauw 与 “Imano双生” 共同演绎，展示了 Loewe 2018 春夏女装成衣系列。画册为摄影师受邀为品牌独家创作。艺术家 Fumiko Imano 擅长通过摄影、视频及造型展现自拍肖像。她的“双生”系列是其对自身成长经历的情感反射。因为感到孤独， Imano 开始剪切并粘贴 35 毫米的肖像，在一个虚构的孪生姐妹的陪伴下，创作出看似像偷拍照的拼贴画。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105353lpydZi91J3gAH7Ga.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669792\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105407oRHLTIctXOPC8k2F.png\" data-ratio=\"0.661706\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105416k4SomPyIA9XULvdV.png\" data-ratio=\"0.674089\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105416wP83CYcTnktMKQV1.png\" data-ratio=\"1.385744\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111105502na9WMLeCuv8BGmHE.png\" data-ratio=\"0.661706\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801111055043f4KJ7rnboX1kU85.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669792\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Loewe</p>"}